    <title>ssh免密登录</title>
    <link href="https://whmsec.github.io/2021/02/24/ssh%E5%85%8D%E5%AF%86%E7%99%BB%E5%BD%95/"/>
    <id>https://whmsec.github.io/2021/02/24/ssh%E5%85%8D%E5%AF%86%E7%99%BB%E5%BD%95/</id>
    <published>2021-02-24T06:52:56.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-02-24T07:36:28.364Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote class="blockquote-center">            <i class="fa fa-quote-left"></i>            <p>生如蝼蚁，当立鸿鹄之志；</p><p>命薄似纸，应有不屈之心；</p><p>乾坤未定，你我都是黑马！</p>            <i class="fa fa-quote-right"></i>          </blockquote><span id="more"></span><h3 id="0x01-前言"><a href="#0x01-前言" class="headerlink" title="0x01  前言"></a>0x01  前言</h3><p>每次ssh登陆linux服务器都要手动输入账号密码,很麻烦。于是记录一下linux免密登录的方法。</p><h3 id="0x02-ssh免密登录linux服务器"><a href="#0x02-ssh免密登录linux服务器" class="headerlink" title="0x02  ssh免密登录linux服务器"></a>0x02  ssh免密登录linux服务器</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">在windows的用户目录下创建.ssh目录:mkdir ~&#x2F;.ssh</span><br><span class="line">cd .ssh</span><br><span class="line">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C &quot;1292678975@qq.com&quot;,后面接3个回车</span><br><span class="line">登录linux服务器</span><br><span class="line">mkdir ~&#x2F;.ssh</span><br><span class="line">vi ~&#x2F;.ssh&#x2F;authorized_keys</span><br><span class="line">把刚才.ssh目录下生成的id_rsa.pub文件发送到linux根目录</span><br><span class="line">cat ~&#x2F;id_rsa.pub &gt;&gt; ~&#x2F;.ssh&#x2F;authorized_keys</span><br><span class="line">删除服务器的id_rsa.pub:rm ~&#x2F;id_rsa.pub</span><br><span class="line">重启ssh服务:service sshd restart</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="0x03-配置ssh会话永不过期"><a href="#0x03-配置ssh会话永不过期" class="headerlink" title="0x03  配置ssh会话永不过期"></a>0x03  配置ssh会话永不过期</h3><figure class="highlight txt"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vi /etc/ssh/sshd_config</span><br><span class="line">ClientAliveInterval 60</span><br><span class="line">ClientAliveCountMax 3</span><br><span class="line">service sshd restart</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;blockquote class=&quot;blockquote-center&quot;&gt;
            &lt;i class=&quot;fa fa-quote-left&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;
            &lt;p&gt;生如蝼蚁，当立鸿鹄之志；&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;命薄似纸，应有不屈之心；&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;乾坤未定，你我都是黑马！&lt;/p&gt;

